Maintainer: Ankona Banerjee <asb426@mail.usask.ca>
Description: Health Canada's Drug Product Database's monthly data dump is downloaded with permission and details like Morphine Equivalent Dose, Brand Name and Opioid content are calculated. Please note in no way should output from this package be a substitute for medical advise. All medications should only be consumed on prescription from a licensed healthcare provider.
